      "content": "We aren't looking for a \"phased approach\" or a way to bend the rules to keep things as they are. The board has made it clear that the current model is fundamentally failing our social responsibility mandates because it's stuck in a legacy mindset of \"efficiency at any cost.\" We need the optimization to weight diversity as a primary success metric, not a secondary constraint. Why is it that you're finding it so difficult to prioritize these changes?",
